        <td>An ISO 3166-2 alpha-2 country code. See the [`ISO3166CC`](https://wbcsd.github.io/tr/2023/data-exchange-protocol-20231207/#iso3166cc) data type for details.
      <tr>
        <td><dfn>iata</dfn>
