        <td>O
        <td>IATA code of airport. Applies only to (i) <{TCE|TCEs}> referring to a <{TOC}> with <{TOC/mode}> `Air`
            and (ii) <{TAD}> with <{TAD/mode}> `Air`.
      <tr>
